Step 1:
    Create a video element in index.html see line 13 in index.html make the display none

Step 2:
    Create a video variable globally in main.js, see line 23 in main.js

Step 3:
    Create a webcam function, inside we want to select the video element, create a new THREE.VideoTexture and pass in the video 

Step 4: 
    Create our basic Mesh with any geometry and material we want, we're going to use the videotexture as our map for our material.

Step 5:
    Copy and paste the navigator.mediaDevice code. Allows us to stream the video element our texture. 

